data.description: BRIGHT AND COMFORTABLE INTERIOR TOWNHOME IN CONSTANT FRIENDSHIP WITH 2 SPACIOUS BEDROOMS. THE UPPER LEVEL HAS WIDE VINYL PLANK FLOORING IN BOTH BEDROOMS, LANDING AND STAIRWAY. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH EN-SUITE HAS VAULTED CEILINGS, SKYLIGHTS AND DUAL CLOSETS. THERE ARE 2 FULL AND 2 HALF BATHS IN THE HOUSE SO EVERY FLOOR HAS A BATHROOM. THE MAIN LEVEL HAS AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH CERAMIC TILE FLOORING WHICH DISPLAYS TRANSITION DECORATIVE DESIGN, HUGE FAMILY ROOM WITH ELECTRIC FIREPLACE AND DINING AREA WITH SLIDER TO THE REAR YARD. FINISHED BASEMENT WITH NEW CARPET, PAINT, UPDATED HALF BATH AND RECENT PROFESSIONAL WATERPROOFING IN 2021 COMPLETE WITH WARRANTY. THIS ALLOWS FOR PLENTY OF ROOM FOR A THIRD BEDROOM. OTHER UPDATES INCLUDE NEW ROOF IN 2020, HOT WATER HEATER 2020, FRONT WINDOWS, UPPER LEVEL WINDOWS  AND SLIDER IN 2022. SHOW AND SELL! PLEASE TRY TO ATTEND THE OPEN HOUSE AS THERE WILL BE RESTRICTED TIMES FOR SHOWINGS.
